Ask HN: Examples of great PWAs
text:
Looking for examples of best-in-class of PWAs, a few of my favorites listed below.

Pinafore, a Mastodon client: https://pinafore.social/

Resilient Web Design, a PWA book by Jeremy Keith: https://resilientwebdesign.com

2048, the game: https://2048game.com

I see a bunch of praise for the Starbucks PWA, but I wasn’t too impressed: https://app.starbucks.com/
